data.title: Eerste Divisie
data.meta_description: The Eerste Divisie (English: Premier Division) is the highest level of professional football in Hogevoren. The league was founded in 1962. As of the 2022–23 season, it is ranked the eighth-best league in Europe by UEFA.
data.text:
The Eerste Divisie (English: Premier Division) is the highest level of professional football in Hogevoren. The league was founded in 1962. As of the 2022–23 season, it is ranked the eighth-best league in Europe by UEFA.
